{"tid":1769380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續紅色五毛化警示","createTime":"2019-12-05T00:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T01:29:34.000Z","uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0670aaa60cb0912994229c97033fdac040d63c8b","tid":1769380,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:32:37.000Z","msg":"連續一星期的五毛風向，繼續以推動內部矛盾為主軸<br />\n<br />\n1. 全面質疑黃色經濟圈，包括食物或價值質素，藍扮黃店令人對所有黃店存戒心<br />\n<br />\n2. 繼續老調重彈質疑612基金，基本上就係打稻草人方式去批鬥<br />\n<br />\n3. 對任何準備立法會，或特首提名委員會的積極方案潑冷水<br />\n<br />\n4.不斷濫用condom 一詞轉移大家視線到無關痛癢的議題上面<br />\n<br />\n5. 繼續以推動無差別暴力作為抗爭的唯一手法<br />\n<br />\n值得一提：最近連仔幾次update,  好似成功趕走左一堆疆屍account。當然，又可能係疆屍account 未出動。<br />\n<br />\n而家班五毛除左<span style=\"color: red;\">五味冰火，思覺脫，瓏美仔</span>呢幾個出晒名的account 之外，就係一堆之前半疆屍的account。<br />\n<br />\n重要提醒：五毛疆屍account 絕大多數以女user account 形式出現"},{"pid":"add351688111472e44fc622d8f03f086b962cb65","tid":1769380,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffe38a98774c39c382a846180508f76c840af01","tid":1769380,"uid":198590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:54:30.000Z","msg":"最近五毛會開大量有爭議性的post 吸引大家討論<br />\n（一個account 一日約20個）<br />\n主題有時會有分化的情況<br />\n目的可能係唔想影響大家12.8的討論<br />\n<br />\n希望大家明白<br />\n時代變 環境變<br />\n好似而家出去發夢<br />\n已經冇晒鐵欄<br />\n路障由欄變磚，磚變火<br />\n<br />\n我地已經唔可以好似6-7月咁<br />\n成個熱門都係行動<br />\n一來因為我地的戰線愈來愈多<br />\n二來因為五毛網軍長期集結<br />\n會用 洗板 回帶 假新聞 ddos等等方式<br />\n<br />\n冇大台<br />\n人人都更加應保持理智<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n12.8 維園見"},{"pid":"7abe585af7dd8e537d44828e456c4346bf05d543","tid":1769380,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:56:08.000Z","msg":"講野唔岩你聽就話人五毛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17099d9c969bd4f43721cb0dea170c5fad9a5c54","tid":1769380,"uid":188183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:59:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e7f36c0e3d65f73b025906f11b8e4f00fc2cd16","tid":1769380,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7abe585af7dd8e537d44828e456c4346bf05d543","tid":1769380,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T00:56:08.000Z","msg":"講野唔岩你聽就話人五毛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"thx 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caab166ec3d09e554d44e87635ab1710223cf37","tid":1769380,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}